    <content><![CDATA[<p>记录Git的常见用法</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h4 id="Git-基础"><a href="#Git-基础" class="headerlink" title="Git 基础"></a>Git 基础</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$ </span><span class="language-bash"><span class="built_in">cd</span> &lt;folder_name&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta"># </span><span class="language-bash">初始化一个 Git 仓库，该命令会在目录中生成一个 .git 文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$ </span><span class="language-bash">git init</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta"># </span><span class="language-bash">添加文件或者文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$ </span><span class="language-bash">git add &lt;file_name&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
